{"tid":2225290,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"༄༊࿆中國數間百億級晶片投資項目停止༊࿆࿐","createTime":"2020-10-01T07:59:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-01T09:34:45.000Z","uid":38539,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"ff4160ad2849ad1298262703821525bf6ee42e36","tid":2225290,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T07:59:59.000Z","msg":"中國被發現有數間上百億投資額的晶片公司、工廠已停擺、爛尾，人去樓空。<br />\n但2020上半年又有20個新的半導體項目，合計投入600億人民幣。<br />\n<br />\n1.南京德科瑪<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f32Wmaj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff32Wmaj.jpg&h=1caf37ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n廠區雜草叢生，連牆壁都還沒蓋出來。<br />\n<br />\n成立於2015年12月，號稱媲美台積電，第一期投資就達25億人民幣，但實際到位的資金僅1/10。<br />\n南京地方政府入場接刀，成為「被股東」，多方找尋投資者無果，目前仍然難以重啟項目。德科瑪負責人已遭限制出境、限制消費。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1J05eBe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1J05eBe.png&h=8b9d75b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.eet-china.com/news/202007101056.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eet-china.com%2Fnews%2F202007101056.html&d=2MheXYw%2FBwPqfvV%2BE34w134WTS3z8ocQ7DCXl2btf88%3D&h=56a67b85\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.eet-china.com/news/202007101056.html</a><br />\n<br />\n2.成都格芯積體電路製造公司<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BFp2gJY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBFp2gJY.jpg&h=8ea3c4a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n曾受中國官媒力捧的項目。<br />\n<br />\n2017年由「格羅方德」和地方政府合作的項目，規劃投資90億美金，號稱是格羅方德在全球投資規模最大、技術最先進的項目。<br />\n規劃約24000坪的廠區，廠內已空無一人，能搬的已搬空。唯一的員工是門口的保全。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LXvXP97.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLXvXP97.png&h=ad628cd6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://finance.technews.tw/2020/05/19/globalfoundries-in-china-2/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffinance.technews.tw%2F2020%2F05%2F19%2Fglobalfoundries-in-china-2%2F&d=2MheXYw%2FBwPqfvV%2BE34w134WTS3z8ocQ7DCXl2btf88%3D&h=9ece64ac\" target=\"_blank\">https://finance.technews.tw/2020/05/19/globalfoundries-in-china-2/</a><br />\n<br />\n3.陝西坤同半導體<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Hgr4u36.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHgr4u36.jpg&h=40624edd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n連個廠區的樣子都還沒出現。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cz4mxhy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fcz4mxhy.jpg&h=18fcbea7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n公司負責人稱我們還沒倒，只是經營比較困難。<br />\n<br />\n成立於2018年，註冊資本達139億人民幣，預計投資金額達400億人民幣。<br />\n為中國首個AMOLED生產基地。<br />\n員工規模稱達5000人，但實際最高的時候僅300人不到，據傳可能都是建築工跟湊數演戲的工程師。從2019年12月開始發不出薪水，員工的保險也繳不出來。並開始遣散員工將項目終結。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BpteSpg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBpteSpg.png&h=4c6124d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.sina.com.tw/article/20200506/35070050.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sina.com.tw%2Farticle%2F20200506%2F35070050.html&d=2MheXYw%2FBwPqfvV%2BE34w134WTS3z8ocQ7DCXl2btf88%3D&h=94a88136\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.sina.com.tw/article/20200506/35070050.html</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.chainnews.com/zh-hant/articles/769539923558.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chainnews.com%2Fzh-hant%2Farticles%2F769539923558.htm&d=2MheXYw%2FBwPqfvV%2BE34w134WTS3z8ocQ7DCXl2btf88%3D&h=d3268777\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.chainnews.com/zh-hant/articles/769539923558.htm</a><br />\n4.江蘇德淮半導體<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9bOngKq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9bOngKq.jpg&h=71c2e65b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2016年成立，預計投入450億人民幣。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xPbzShS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxPbzShS.jpg&h=33d73ce8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n實際到帳46億人民幣，皆由地方政府投入。用於購買兩台Nikon二手曝光機、Intel二手曝光機、員工薪資等開銷。<br />\n2019年員工及廠商向地方政府投訴欠薪欠款，地方政府介入公司。至今一片晶圓都沒生出來。地方政府拒絕再投入任何資金。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4xmoLKD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4xmoLKD.png&h=7ae9617b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://finance.sina.com/bg/tech/technews/cb/2019-11-08/doc-ifzqrxyc5351081.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffinance.sina.com%2Fbg%2Ftech%2Ftechnews%2Fcb%2F2019-11-08%2Fdoc-ifzqrxyc5351081.shtml&d=2MheXYw%2FBwPqfvV%2BE34w134WTS3z8ocQ7DCXl2btf88%3D&h=0cc561ba\" target=\"_blank\">https://finance.sina.com/bg/tech/technews/cb/2019-11-08/doc-ifzqrxyc5351081.shtml</a><br />\n<br />\n5.貴州華芯通半導體<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UbJKu4H.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUbJKu4H.jpg&h=2e41b95d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NyXZ3pR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNyXZ3pR.jpg&h=26ffc7c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2016年由貴州政府與高通合作發起的項目。被稱為明星企業、中美晶片戰略合作。目標生產ARM架構伺服器CPU，希望實現中國晶圓自主可控。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sC6ssRD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsC6ssRD.jpg&h=b32ee349&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2018年推出第一代CPU，稱年產量可達150萬顆。此投入金額達5.7億美元。隨後在2019年宣布項目停止(倒閉)。<br />\n執行長表示：一言難盡。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u9RoLKV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu9RoLKV.png&h=9e67a0f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://tech.sina.com.cn/it/2019-04-28/doc-ihvhiqax5453816.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftech.sina.com.cn%2Fit%2F2019-04-28%2Fdoc-ihvhiqax5453816.shtml&d=2MheXYw%2FBwPqfvV%2BE34w134WTS3z8ocQ7DCXl2btf88%3D&h=84347b42\" target=\"_blank\">https://tech.sina.com.cn/it/2019-04-28/doc-ihvhiqax5453816.shtml</a><br />\n6.武漢弘芯半導體<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1S1cDYt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1S1cDYt.jpg&h=f0270f6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2017年規劃投資金額1280億人民幣。邀請台積電元老蔣尚義擔任執行長。<br />\n預計生產14奈米製程的晶圓，月產量3萬片。也預計生產7奈米製程的晶圓，月產量同樣是3萬片。對此武漢地方政府也非常重視，據傳政府已投入153億人民幣。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PRXjiX1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPRXjiX1.jpg&h=3e708006&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n風光迎接高端曝光機進廠。同時向銀行抵押曝光機用於貸款。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2mGToqn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2mGToqn.jpg&h=d81044da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CAAdowX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCAAdowX.png&h=0cc62175&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200908/YQHJ6A7XXFEFJJFN6HDR73KHKA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200908%2FYQHJ6A7XXFEFJJFN6HDR73KHKA%2F&d=2MheXYw%2FBwPqfvV%2BE34w134WTS3z8ocQ7DCXl2btf88%3D&h=a50ff509\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200908%2FYQHJ6A7XXFEFJJFN6HDR73KHKA%2F&h=2503045b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200908/YQHJ6A7XXFEFJJFN6HDR73KHKA/</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://disp.cc/b/163-cNkL\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdisp.cc%2Fb%2F163-cNkL&d=2MheXYw%2FBwPqfvV%2BE34w134WTS3z8ocQ7DCXl2btf88%3D&h=60cb92b3\" target=\"_blank\">https://disp.cc/b/163-cNkL</a><br />\nPTT整合咗近排一啲中國晶片大廠爛尾收皮資料<br />\n我補返啲醬汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75856f50c99a0ec2710d854127daf22446bc9d37","tid":2225290,"uid":122275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T08:05:34.000Z","msg":"GDP GOGOGO"},{"pid":"5dc6a6ae2249b2f5e5cf28f91ed4d7fe1b3c8a1e","tid":2225290,"uid":30067,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T08:07:40.000Z","msg":"貪哂d錢啦屌<br />\n連登仔笑人公司一事無成<br />\n個老細袋幾億環遊世界"},{"pid":"e67dcc79a793a11d4800cc203a0abb64eabf3f3a","tid":2225290,"uid":13343,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T08:08:35.000Z","msg":"輸喇輸喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e103e72b7dbf1766ab4e1f37400ccf3cdbe0ea0","tid":2225290,"uid":58552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T08:08:57.000Z","msg":"雞棚<br />\n用大煉晶做騙局<br />\n去銀行借錢<br />\n之後走佬"},{"pid":"89d872cbf4f0e6d27e3651d0f1f11321152d55f8","tid":2225290,"uid":52675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T08:09:14.000Z","msg":"黨員:fap fap<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4dc8849ca088071aba6d7fc2a51b9ee18006649","tid":2225290,"uid":133383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T08:22:15.000Z","msg":"鷄棚項目最多<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28d5986695b2fdf37831a872ac8ac03fbcd1450f","tid":2225290,"uid":271807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T08:44:38.000Z","msg":"無問題，9萬億黎緊"},{"pid":"59a1d0e05bc6c105cf806022090871bed6f42660","tid":2225290,"uid":13343,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T08:47:15.000Z","msg":"仆街食人血饅頭 <br />\n<br />\n晶片手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"466565180e7016e319ac31064822025116596c21","tid":2225290,"uid":249094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5dc6a6ae2249b2f5e5cf28f91ed4d7fe1b3c8a1e","tid":2225290,"uid":30067,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T08:07:40.000Z","msg":"貪哂d錢啦屌<br />\n連登仔笑人公司一事無成<br />\n個老細袋幾億環遊世界"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T08:50:05.000Z","msg":"讓一部分人富起來<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n終国又然<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},