png&h=422a100c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T09:34:45.000Z","msg":"中華移民共和國唔係得個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}